source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Conservation Elements: Special Designations
source.description: This map shows special designations in the ecoregion, derived from the CBI Protected Areas Database, National Conservation Easements Database, Roadless Areas, BLM NLCS Wilderness Areas, and BLM ACECs.
